O '''Mateo Maximoff''' (opretele [[17 yanuara]] [[1917]], [[Barselona]] - [[24 novembra]] [[1999]]) sas ekh Romano lekhavno (pe [[franchikanes]]).

Lesko dad sas [[Rom]] [[Kalderash]], leski day, [[Manush]]ni (e Romane manusha andar e [[Franchiya]]). O dad siklyardya les te drabarel (chitisarel), lekhavel (rimol) thay te ginavel. May phendya leske but pa e [[Rusiya]], pa o puranipen le Kalderashengo, pa kaver Romane nyamurya. Vov mulo kana Mateo sas 14 [[bersh]]engo. Deatunchara, o terno Mateo trebulas te kerel but buti te pravarel pes thay leske phralen thay phenyan.

1936 bershesko, kana shirdya o [[Andruno Maripen e Spaniyako]], vov thay peski familiya gele kay Franchiya. Ando 1940to bersh, von phandavde, e sirale phenindoi ke si spionurya. Beshlen 42 [[dives]]a andekh lager e "spionengo", palal kodya e sirale bichhalde len ko lager e "Jipsiyengo", ando [[thanipen]] Tarbes, vi may palal ko Lannemazan.

Palal o [[Duito Maripen Lumiyako]], vov beshlo andi Franchiya. Lekhavdo deshuekh lila, ambolde pe deshushtar [[chhib]]a.

Vov sas vi [[evangelikani khangeri|evangelikano]] [[pastoro]] thai amboldyas pe [[Romanes]] o [[Nevo Testamento]].

